metadata.name: OVERTHINKING
metadata.description:
OVERTHINKING

1/1 Edition

Graphite Pencil mix Digital Art

Your overthinking about me is not my business, it's you with your head! Because I will always be kind to keep my mind beautiful.

Tools traditional art:

Paper A3 (30 cm x 40 cm)
Graphite Pencils (2B, 4B, 8B)
Mechanical Eraser
Brush
Paper Stump

The result of traditional art was combined with manual digital art.

3000 x 4000 px
